<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Bargle</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-20 17:51:45</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>For large troll and ogre shadowknights, this can really save your butt sometimes. I've gotten STUCK in some places and this has been my escape route. If I had been a warrior, I would need to either die, ask for a teleport, or wait a long time for NPCs to move.<BR>
<BR>
Example: Try taking an ogre and squeezing through the underwater entrance to the smuggleres cave in Highpass Hold. You won't be able to get back the same way without this spell, or falling a LONG way down.</font></td></tr></table>
